<font color="yellow">What's wrong with that?</font>

867
01:04:04,870 --> 01:04:06,970
<font color="yellow">What should I do, Mum?</font>

868
01:04:09,510 --> 01:04:11,970
<font color="yellow">Poor Hee Ja.</font>

869
01:04:12,870 --> 01:04:14,940
<font color="yellow">What should we do?</font>

870
01:05:06,410 --> 01:05:08,470
<font color="yellow">You're wearing what I bought you.</font>

871
01:05:08,470 --> 01:05:09,670
<font color="yellow">I am.</font>

872
01:05:17,470 --> 01:05:20,770
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with you? Why did you want to die?</font>

873
01:05:21,840 --> 01:05:24,420
<font color="yellow">I can't even change a light bulb.</font>

874
01:05:24,420 --> 01:05:26,270
<font color="yellow">The doctor said I'm delusional.</font>

875
01:05:27,340 --> 01:05:30,210
<font color="yellow">If I end up with dementia,</font>

876
01:05:30,910 --> 01:05:32,540
<font color="yellow">Min Ho will get angry with me.</font>

877
01:05:33,970 --> 01:05:35,570
<font color="yellow">Then he'll get exhausted.</font>

878
01:05:36,940 --> 01:05:37,940
<font color="yellow">That's why.</font>

879
01:05:38,340 --> 01:05:39,710
<font color="yellow">You wanted to die with me.</font>

880
01:05:40,140 --> 01:05:41,540
<font color="yellow">What about me, then?</font>

881
01:05:42,170 --> 01:05:43,210
<font color="yellow">What about me?</font>

882
01:05:44,110 --> 01:05:45,210
<font color="yellow">You're a terrible friend.</font>

883
01:05:46,610 --> 01:05:47,610
<font color="yellow">You're right.</font>

884
01:05:48,440 --> 01:05:50,510
<font color="yellow">I have you, don't I?</font>

885
01:06:18,340 --> 01:06:19,980
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

886
01:06:22,980 --> 01:06:24,010
<font color="yellow">Church?</font>

887
01:06:25,710 --> 01:06:28,240
<font color="yellow">To give them the rosaries you made?</font>

888
01:06:30,310 --> 01:06:31,570
<font color="yellow">What will you do after that?</font>

889
01:06:33,840 --> 01:06:35,870
<font color="yellow">I want to see you, of course.</font>

890
01:06:37,480 --> 01:06:40,070
<font color="yellow">Watch out for the cars and be careful.</font>

891
01:06:41,570 --> 01:06:44,840
<font color="yellow">Go straight home instead of anywhere else.</font>

892
01:06:46,340 --> 01:06:49,170
<font color="yellow">I'll bring some tteokbokki. You like tteokbokki.</font>

893
01:06:50,510 --> 01:06:52,910
<font color="yellow">Okay. See you later.</font>

894
01:07:04,410 --> 01:07:05,810
<font color="yellow">She's going to church.</font>

895
01:07:08,010 --> 01:07:10,010
<font color="yellow">She goes there every Friday.</font>

896
01:07:11,040 --> 01:07:13,670
<font color="yellow">It's the evening trips I'm worried about.</font>

897
01:07:15,310 --> 01:07:17,240
<font color="yellow">She's fine during the day.</font>

898
01:07:19,480 --> 01:07:21,070
<font color="yellow">Let's go and see Min Ho.</font>

899
01:07:22,980 --> 01:07:24,440
<font color="yellow">Let's leave a bit later.</font>

900
01:07:27,980 --> 01:07:29,340
<font color="yellow">I'll wait outside.</font>

901
01:07:57,110 --> 01:07:59,840
<font color="yellow">(Hospital)</font>

902
01:08:07,340 --> 01:08:08,480
<font color="yellow">Then...</font>

903
01:08:09,540 --> 01:08:11,410
<font color="yellow">when can I have surgery?</font>

904
01:08:12,410 --> 01:08:14,110
<font color="yellow">You need it soon.</font>

905
01:08:15,270 --> 01:08:16,910
<font color="yellow">But my schedule's...</font>

906
01:08:19,340 --> 01:08:20,340
<font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

907
01:08:21,540 --> 01:08:23,640
<font color="yellow">What? Why are the onions rotten?</font>

908
01:08:25,670 --> 01:08:26,980
<font color="yellow">Throw them out.</font>

909
01:08:26,980 --> 01:08:29,270
<font color="yellow">Call the Jeju Brothers and ask them...</font>

910
01:08:29,270 --> 01:08:30,910
<font color="yellow">to bring some urgently.</font>

911
01:08:31,940 --> 01:08:35,010
<font color="yellow">Don't try to save anything. Throw everything out.</font>

912
01:08:35,710 --> 01:08:37,410
<font color="yellow">You'll just waste time.</font>

913
01:08:37,770 --> 01:08:39,670
<font color="yellow">I'm the boss, not you.</font>

914
01:08:42,040 --> 01:08:45,840
<font color="yellow">Basically, you're in the worst place possible.</font>

915
01:08:46,810 --> 01:08:47,980
<font color="yellow">It's not just the liver.</font>

916
01:08:48,540 --> 01:08:50,340
<font color="yellow">It has spread all over.</font>

917
01:08:51,710 --> 01:08:56,410
<font color="yellow">(Yeong Won)</font>

918
01:09:04,340 --> 01:09:06,040
<font color="yellow">If it's so urgent,</font>

919
01:09:06,480 --> 01:09:08,710
<font color="yellow">why must I wait three weeks?</font>

920
01:09:09,410 --> 01:09:12,040
<font color="yellow">He just wants me to die, not live.</font>

921
01:09:13,810 --> 01:09:16,070
<font color="yellow">But then again, I'm not his only patient.</font>

922
01:09:24,570 --> 01:09:26,570
<font color="yellow">(Wan)</font>

923
01:09:30,440 --> 01:09:31,740
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

924
01:09:31,740 --> 01:09:32,770
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

925
01:09:34,540 --> 01:09:35,740
<font color="yellow">Sorry.</font>

926
01:09:35,740 --> 01:09:36,770
<font color="yellow">"What?"</font>

927
01:09:37,910 --> 01:09:38,910
<font color="yellow">"What?"</font>

928
01:09:39,840 --> 01:09:41,980
<font color="yellow">Is that all you can say right now?</font>

929
01:09:44,140 --> 01:09:45,170
<font color="yellow">I'll be there.</font>

930
01:09:45,570 --> 01:09:48,670
<font color="yellow">You know how busy this place gets at lunchtime.</font>

931
01:09:49,270 --> 01:09:51,770
<font color="yellow">I dropped by on my way to the publisher's.</font>

932
01:09:53,110 --> 01:09:55,640
<font color="yellow">I can't leave when everyone's so busy.</font>

933
01:09:55,640 --> 01:09:58,210
<font color="yellow">Where on earth are you?</font>

934
01:09:59,240 --> 01:10:00,240
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

935
01:10:01,480 --> 01:10:02,570
<font color="yellow">Shopping?</font>

936
01:10:04,710 --> 01:10:05,740
<font color="yellow">Take this.</font>

937
01:10:07,480 --> 01:10:09,110
<font color="yellow">Why did you go shopping?</font>

938
01:10:09,910 --> 01:10:12,480
<font color="yellow">Are you really dating someone?</font>

939
01:10:13,240 --> 01:10:14,240
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

940
01:10:15,170 --> 01:10:16,170
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

941
01:10:18,670 --> 01:10:19,840
<font color="yellow">Where's our jjamppong?</font>

942
01:10:19,840 --> 01:10:20,870
<font color="yellow">It's coming.</font>

943
01:10:20,870 --> 01:10:22,980
<font color="yellow">Where's the jjamppong for table nine?</font>

944
01:10:22,980 --> 01:10:24,110
<font color="yellow">It's ready.</font>

945
01:12:32,440 --> 01:12:35,540
<font color="yellow">We had cotton candy</font>

946
01:12:36,540 --> 01:12:39,070
<font color="yellow">When I blew on it</font>

947
01:12:39,840 --> 01:12:41,870
<font color="yellow">It made a hole</font>

948
01:12:42,610 --> 01:12:45,140
<font color="yellow">That big blob of cotton candy</font>

949
01:13:21,940 --> 01:13:23,710
<font color="yellow">(Dear My Friends)</font>

950
01:13:24,340 --> 01:13:25,410
<font color="yellow">I saw it.</font>

951
01:13:25,980 --> 01:13:28,630
<font color="yellow">You have to be stronger than anyone.</font>

952
01:13:28,630 --> 01:13:30,710
<font color="yellow">Why do you keep calling me?</font>

953
01:13:30,710 --> 01:13:32,910
<font color="yellow">Answer me. Where are you right now?</font>

954
01:13:32,910 --> 01:13:34,770
<font color="yellow">Do you want me to tell Wan?</font>

955
01:13:35,940 --> 01:13:37,010
<font color="yellow">Or do you want to tell her?</font>

956
01:13:37,340 --> 01:13:40,010
<font color="yellow">Do you hate that I like your mum?</font>

957
01:13:40,340 --> 01:13:42,840
<font color="yellow">Well, there's nothing you can do about it...</font>

958
01:13:42,840 --> 01:13:44,010
<font color="yellow">because I like your mum...</font>

959
01:13:44,980 --> 01:13:46,440
<font color="yellow">a lot.</font>

960
01:13:47,510 --> 01:13:49,170
<font color="yellow">Who told you to bear it alone?</font>

961
01:13:49,640 --> 01:13:51,310
<font color="yellow">Why am I your baggage?</font>

962
01:13:52,240 --> 01:13:54,180
<font color="yellow">Of course. I'm doing well.</font>

963
01:13:54,180 --> 01:13:57,240
<font color="yellow">I'm so scared.</font>

964
01:13:57,240 --> 01:13:58,610
<font color="yellow">It's upsetting me.</font>

965
01:13:58,610 --> 01:14:02,270
<font color="yellow">I want to live. I do.</font>

